    {
      "name": "Профиль и размеры",
      "text": "Side-on, the proportions read true. 3.4 metres at the shoulder. 4.9 metres nose to tail. Heavier than a Manhattan delivery truck, low enough that tourists climb on its back for the photo. Di Modica wanted the silhouette of an animal mid-charge — not a monument — and the choice of pose forced everything else: a heavy front quarter, a planted hind, the centre of gravity dropped forward.",
