    {
      "name": "Вид сзади",
      "text": "From behind, the bull keeps the same charging momentum — tail and rump and the slope of a back arched for the strike. The most-touched spot of all is here: visitors duck beneath the belly, sit for a photograph, and steady themselves by leaning on the joints of the hind legs — which is why those joints are polished smooth too. Power, virility, force — the same animal symbol, told from a different angle.",
